<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CampCritic</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-r4NyP46KrjDleawBgD5tp8Y7UzmLA05oM1iAEQ17CSuDqnUK2+k9luXQOfXJCJ4I" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
</head>

<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
        <header class="mb-auto">
            <div>
                <h3 class="float-md-left mb-0">CampCritic</h3>
                <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-right">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/campgrounds">Campgrounds</a>
                    <% if(!currentUser) { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                    <% } %>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="px-3">
            <h1 style="text-align: center;" class="mb-4">CampCritic!</h1>
                <p>Welcome to <strong>"CampCritic"</strong>, your go-to source for honest and reliable reviews of campgrounds
                    from around the world. Whether you're an experienced camper or just starting out, our reviews will help you
                    find the perfect campground for your next outdoor adventure.
                </p>
                <p>At CampCritic, we believe that the great outdoors should be accessible to everyone, and that's why
                    we're dedicated to providing thorough and unbiased reviews of campgrounds from every corner of the globe. We
                    take the time to visit each campground in person and assess its facilities, location, and overall
                    atmosphere, so you can be sure you're getting the best possible information.</p>
        
                <p> So whether you're planning a weekend getaway or a longer adventure, be sure to check out CampCritic
                    for all the information you need to find the perfect campsite. Happy camping!</p>
        
                    <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold border-white bg-white">View
                        Campgrounds</a>
                </main>

        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy; 2022 </p>
        </footer>


    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-oesi62hOLfzrys4LxRF63OJCXdXDipiYWBnvTl9Y9/TRlw5xlKIEHpNyvvDShgf/"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>